title: Besser mit Zed werden

embed.description: I'm getting better with Zed! Trying out Volibear and Olaf right now, so maybe you'll see some Together's of these Champions in future time :) I hope you enjoy the time with me, please let me know if you have something to tell, I appreciate every comment, even if it's trolling haha!

body: Ich werde so langsam immer besser und besser mit Zed! Noch welche Tipps für mich?
